# Third-party datasheets / schematics / firmware repos here are copyrighted
# vendor IP. They are kept LOCALLY for engineering reference (D-0026 round-1
# Elecrow hardware) but NOT republished in this public repo. Track ONLY our own
# provenance files: this .gitignore, the top-level README.md, and every
# _MANIFEST.md (a name unique to us — third-party trees never use it). Every
# other file — incl. nested third-party README.md/CHANGELOG.md from extracted
# repos — stays ignored. Rehydrate binaries via each _MANIFEST.md.
*
!*/
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!**/_MANIFEST.md
